export default function () {
    return(
        <form action="/members/new" method="post">
            <label>name
                <input type="text" placeholder="type your name" name={"name"}/>
            </label>

            <label>city
                <input type="text" placeholder="type your city" name={"city"}/>
            </label>


            <label>street
                <input type="text" placeholder="type your street" name={"street"}/>
            </label>


                <label>zipcode:
                    <input type="text" placeholder="type your zipcode" name={"zipcode"}/>
                </label>

            <input type="submit" value={"submit"}>Submit</input>
        </form>
    )
}
